snippet.title: Bugs Bunny: Crazy Castle 3 Garden Stages 1-3
snippet.description: First 3 stages in the Garden section of the game.  Each section of the Old Castle has 15 stages (except the last one which has 15).  Collect the 8 keys, eliminate the enemies (or don't) and then unlock the door to progress to the next stage.  We have now completed 3/61 total stages.
